    "title": {
      "rendered": "12 Must-Follow Nonprofits on Tumblr"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-17336\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"12 Nonprofit Tumblrs\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12-Nonprofit-Tumblrs.jpg?w=568&amp;ssl=1 568w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>If your nonprofit&#8217;s social media strategy is built upon engaging young adults, then you might want to invest some time experimenting with <a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Tumblr</a>. According to a <a href=\"http://www.emarketer.com/article.aspx?R=1011592\" target=\"_blank\">recent study</a>, after Facebook young adults spend more time per day on Tumblr than any other social network. This data will likely surprise many nonprofits, but Tumblr&#8217;s mobile design\u00a0and the unique content blogged on\u00a0Tumblr\u00a0resonates with millennials. That said, below are 12 nonprofit Tumblrs to study and learn from. Be sure to also\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/apps\" target=\"_blank\">download Tumblr&#8217;s mobile app</a>\u00a0to experience the Tumblrs on a mobile device.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Think Progress<br />\n<a href=\"http://think-progress.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">think-progress.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://think-progress.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17158\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/think-progress-tumblr.png?resize=600%2C369\" alt=\"think progress tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/think-progress-tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/think-progress-tumblr.png?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Smithsonian Magazine<br />\n<a href=\"http://smithsonianmag.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">smithsonianmag.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://smithsonianmag.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17230\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Smithsonian-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C300\" alt=\"Smithsonian Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Smithsonian-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Smithsonian-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Sex, Etc.<br />\n<a href=\"http://sexetc.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">sexetc.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://sexetc.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17222\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Sex-Etc.png?resize=600%2C337\" alt=\"Sex Etc\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Sex-Etc.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Sex-Etc.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Pulitzer Center on Crisis Reporting<br />\n<a href=\"http://pulitzercenter.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">pulitzercenter.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://pulitzercenter.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17174\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/pulitzer-center-on-crisis-reporting.png?resize=600%2C338\" alt=\"pulitzer center on crisis reporting\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/pulitzer-center-on-crisis-reporting.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/pulitzer-center-on-crisis-reporting.png?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Pew Research\u00a0Center<br />\n<a href=\"http://pewresearch.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">pewresearch.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://pewresearch.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17232\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Pew-Research-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C325\" alt=\"Pew Research Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Pew-Research-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Pew-Research-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C162&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. OURTIME.org<br />\n<a href=\"http://attndotcom.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">attndotcom.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://attndotcom.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17160\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ourtimeorg-tumblr.png?resize=600%2C369\" alt=\"ourtimeorg tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ourtimeorg-tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ourtimeorg-tumblr.png?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Natural Resources Defense Council<br />\n<a href=\"http://nrdc.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">nrdc.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nrdc.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17226\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NRDC-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C330\" alt=\"NRDC Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NRDC-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NRDC-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. National Public Radio<br />\n<a href=\"http://npr.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">npr.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://npr.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17219\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NPR-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C369\" alt=\"NPR Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NPR-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NPR-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C184&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Museum of Modern Art<br />\n<a href=\"http://moma.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">moma.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://moma.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17224\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MOMA-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C284\" alt=\"MOMA Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MOMA-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/MOMA-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Made In a Free World<br />\n<a href=\"http://madeinafreeworld.tumblr.com\" target=\"_blank\">madeinafreeworld.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://madeinafreeworld.tumblr.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17165\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/made-in-a-free-world-tumblr.png?resize=600%2C329\" alt=\"made in a free world tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/made-in-a-free-world-tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/made-in-a-free-world-tumblr.png?resize=300%2C164&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Gay, Lesbian &amp; Straight Education Network<br />\n<a href=\"http://glsen.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">glsen.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://glsen.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17228\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/GLSEN-Tumblr.png?resize=600%2C313\" alt=\"GLSEN Tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/GLSEN-Tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/GLSEN-Tumblr.png?resize=300%2C156&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">12. CODE.org<br />\n<a href=\"http://codeorg.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">codeorg.tumblr.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://codeorg.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17167\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/code-org-tumblr.png?resize=600%2C274\" alt=\"code org tumblr\" width=\"600\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/code-org-tumblr.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/code-org-tumblr.png?resize=300%2C137&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
